author: Caitlin Oprysko
title: Four more governors announce new restrictions to curb coronavirus
description: Michigan, Maryland, Massachusetts, and Wisconsin all announced new measures.
content:
Republican Govs. Larry Hogan of Maryland and Charlie Baker of Massachusetts stopped short of ordering residents to stay inside, but both on Monday ordered all non-essential businesses in their states closed.
